# Union operator set for all shipped fono models (onnxruntime 1.24.2).
# Merged union of every per-set config (mirror + fono voices + wake-word) so
# the minimal runtime can load EVERY shipped model:
#   - Piper voices (incl. LSTM / MatMulInteger variants)
#   - Kokoro q8f16 (needs Greater(13), If)
#   - openWakeWord wake-word stack: melspectrogram + Google speech_embedding
#     + the per-phrase classifiers. The REAL upstream dscripka classifiers
#     (hey_jarvis/alexa/hey_mycroft v0.1) use a richer op set than a plain MLP:
#     Gemm(13), LayerNormalization, GreaterOrEqual, Clip, If, Cast, plus the
#     melspectrogram/embedding ops MaxPool(12), Log/Pow/ReduceMax/Max/Add/Div(13)
#     and the com.microsoft FusedGemm contrib op.
# Regenerate with scripts/merge-ort-configs.py over the per-set configs, or from
# the full model set via create_reduced_build_config.py --format ORT
# --enable_type_reduction. The wake-word per-set config comes from running
# fono's scripts/gen-ort-models.sh (ALLOW_PARTIAL=1) over the wake graphs +
# the upstream classifiers.
